gw.api.graph.compare

Class EntityGraphPair

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.graph.compare.EntityGraphPair

  • public class EntityGraphPair
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class for matching entities from two graphs. The source graph is the reference, and potential matches for a given source entity will be found from the compare graph.
    Author:
    bspies
